               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t18310908-372-off1905-c2117" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-372-defend2643 t18310908-372-off1905 t18310908-372-verdict1907"></join>
         
               <p>1909. 
               
                  <persName id="t18310908-372-defend2643" type="defendantName">
                     JOSEPH 
                     UNWIN
                  <interp inst="t18310908-372-defend2643" type="surname" value="UNWIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-defend2643" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-defend2643" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-defend2643" type="age" value="27"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18310908-372-off1905" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-off1905" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-off1905" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310908-372-cd1906" type="crimeDate">2nd of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-372-off1905 t18310908-372-cd1906"></join>, 1 cap, value 7s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18310908-372-victim2644" type="victimName">
                  Mary Ann 
                  Pain
               <interp inst="t18310908-372-victim2644" type="surname" value="Pain"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-victim2644" type="given" value="Mary Ann"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-victim2644" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-372-off1905 t18310908-372-victim2644"></join>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-372-person2645">
                  HENRY 
                  LEE
               <interp inst="t18310908-372-person2645" type="surname" value="LEE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-person2645" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-person2645" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I was at Ratcliffhighway, about half-past nine o'clock in the evening of the 7th of September - I saw the prisoner, and watched him to the end of my beat; I then saw him putting something into his pocket - I asked what he had there; he said a cap which he had bought at Poplar, and he had got the money by selling fish - I made inquiries, and found Mrs. Pain; the shopman saw this cap, and identified it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-372-person2646">
                  CHARLES 
                  PIGOTT
               <interp inst="t18310908-372-person2646" type="surname" value="PIGOTT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-person2646" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-person2646" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am in the employ of Mary Ann Pain. This cap is her property; I remember seeing it in he shop, but cannot exactly say when - we did not miss it<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183109080153"></xptr>till I went with the officer, and recognized it; I am quite sure it had not been sold that day or the day before.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18310908-372-verdict1907" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-verdict1907" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 27. - <rs id="t18310908-372-punish1908" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-372-punish1908" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-372-defend2643 t18310908-372-punish1908"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
